{"tid":1920560,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再買中文化遊戲","createTime":"2020-03-11T13:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T23:58:15.000Z","uid":300475,"like":3,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3448693ea864f0d00bdf6129cb7fcb48334cb870","tid":1920560,"uid":300475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T13:58:51.000Z","msg":"出得中文化遊戲既公司包括出版同代理都係為左賣去大陸市場 未必真係藍 但係冇可能係黃 寶源就係好好既例子<br />\n第二 QC既問題 好多中文化遊戲 特典中國製造唔再講 翻譯都係搵大陸公司做 玩落果陣大陸味臭到核爆 <br />\n<br />\n鐘意打機既大家除左搵黃店買game之外 記得留意下代理同出版公司 最好就買翻歐美版或者日文版 當學下英文/日文啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正常中文版同時發行既遊戲就算買歐美/日版都可以轉中文玩 詳細可以睇下game盒後面 歐美/日版語言都有機會有中文<br />\n<br />\n歐美版唔太清楚 但日文版好多都可以係Amazon co jp買到仲可以寄海外<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">康復香港，時代抗疫</span></strong>"},{"pid":"7206ee7ed7226f065c1b55869121ec26fa1dd17c","tid":1920560,"uid":250511,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T13:59:38.000Z","msg":"話你on9怕你嬲"},{"pid":"19ddbfee0af6361a4b258fa029010ec89b41b499","tid":1920560,"uid":190817,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T14:02:53.000Z","msg":"ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知唔知自己講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b00849928440ea50ec02a44a08e6f8f5e7afb14","tid":1920560,"uid":147467,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T14:04:13.000Z","msg":"遊戲公司心諗黃你老母<br />\n你up乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁watch dog 2我要真普選算唔算黃<br />\n咁ubisoft係咪黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36c51c306a73ea9c6a37abbe3592e1ce84521d2","tid":1920560,"uid":276382,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T14:04:48.000Z","msg":"其實一般都係搵台灣公司做<br />\n有frd接過幾份ubi嘅freelance翻譯<br />\n條team都係香港人同台灣人"},{"pid":"34cf35a78881e5319d98e78475240d8cb8170b47","tid":1920560,"uid":129475,"li